@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### Config Controller Tests

### Get Config
GET {{baseUrl}}/config
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Environment Variables
GET {{baseUrl}}/config/getEnvVars
Content-Type: application/json

### Food Controller Tests

### Get All Food Items
GET {{baseUrl}}/food
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Food by ID (e.g., ID 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/food/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Create Food Item
POST {{baseUrl}}/food
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 0,
  "name": "Pizza",
  "description": "Delicious cheese pizza",
  "price": 12.99
}

### Update Food Item
PUT {{baseUrl}}/food
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Margherita Pizza",
  "description": "Classic Italian pizza with fresh mozzarella",
  "price": 14.99
}

### Delete Food Item (e.g., ID 1)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/food/1
Content-Type: application/json
